{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/webpack/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<ul>\n<li>bundler란?</li>\n<li>Webpack이란?</li>\n<li>Babel과 Webpack 함께 사용하기</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"bundler란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#bundler%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"bundler란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>bundler란?</h2>\n<p>웹 사이트를 만들다보면 js, css, img 등 수 많은 파일들이 생겨난다. 웹 사이트 로딩 시 많은 파일들이 다운되어지고, 서버와의 접속이 많아져 애플리케이션의 로딩이 느려진다.</p>\n<p>각각의 서로 다른 패키지들이 서로 같은 이름을 가진 변수, 함수를 사용할 수 있다.\n이는 예상치 못한 충돌을 발생시킨다.</p>\n<p>이를 해결하기 위해 등장한 도구들을 <code class=\"language-text\">bundler</code>라 한다.</p>\n<p>bundle? '묶는다' 라는 뜻이다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"대표적인-bundler\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%8C%80%ED%91%9C%EC%A0%81%EC%9D%B8-bundler\" aria-label=\"대표적인 bundler permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>대표적인 bundler</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>webpack</li>\n<li>broserify</li>\n<li>parcel</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"webpack이란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#webpack%EC%9D%B4%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"webpack이란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Webpack이란?</h2>\n<p>의존 관계에 있는 모듈들을 하나의 자바스크립트로 번들링하는 모듈 번들러</p>\n<ul>\n<li>이를 사용하면 의존 모듈이 하나의 파일로 번들링되므로 별도의 모듈 로더가 필요 없다.</li>\n<li>다수의 자바스크립트 파일을 하나의 파일로 번들링하므로 html 파일에서 script 태그로 다수의 자바스크립트 파일을 로드해야 하는 번거로움도 사라진다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"webpack-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#webpack-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"webpack 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Webpack 설치</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># Webpack V4는 webpack-cli를 요구한다</span>\n$ <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> --save-dev webpack webpack-cli</code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"babel과-webpack-함께-사용하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#babel%EA%B3%BC-webpack-%ED%95%A8%EA%BB%98-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"babel과 webpack 함께 사용하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Babel과 Webpack 함께 사용하기</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># babel-loader 설치</span>\n$ <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> --save-dev babel-loader</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"webpackconfigjs-파일-작성하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#webpackconfigjs-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EC%9E%91%EC%84%B1%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"webpackconfigjs 파일 작성하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>webpack.config.js 파일 작성하기</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">webpack.config.js</code>은 Webpack이 실행될 때 참조하는 설정 파일이다.<br>\n프로젝트 루트에 <code class=\"language-text\">webpack.config.js</code> 파일을 생성하고 아래와 같이 작성한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// Webpack이 실행될 때 참조하는 설정 파일</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> path <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'path'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// entry file</span>\n  entry<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./src/js/main.js'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// 컴파일 + 번들링된 js 파일이 저장될 경로와 이름 지정</span>\n  output<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    path<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> path<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">resolve</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>__dirname<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'dist/js'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    filename<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'bundle.js'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\n  module<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    rules<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        test<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token regex\">/\\.js$/</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        include<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>path<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">resolve</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>__dirname<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'src/js'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        exclude<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token regex\">/node_modules/</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        use<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          loader<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'babel-loader'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n          options<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            presets<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'@babel/preset-env'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h4 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 1